                  <p class="- topic/p ">** Chain Pitch for CD100/120 = 44.5 mm</p>
                  <p class="- topic/p ">** Chain Pitch for CD140/160 = 50.8 mm</p>
               </fig>
            </info>
         </step>
      </steps>
